                            <comment id="38102" author="nedbass" created="Thu, 3 May 2012 13:48:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Actually it appears that we were hitting the EXT_ASSERT on lustre/lvfs/fsfilt_ext3.c:977&lt;/p&gt;

